    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    ApplicationCreateRequest
    Request DTO for creating a new application in the Green Global Initiative API.
    ApplicationDetails
    Entity class representing the application details in the Green Global Initiative database.
    ApplicationDetailsDto
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) for holding application details in the Green Global Initiative API.
    ApplicationDetailsRepo
    Repository interface for managing ApplicationDetails entities.
    ApplicationUpdateRequest
    Request DTO for updating an existing application in the Green Global Initiative API.
    ContactUs
    Represents the "Contact Us" form submission in the database.
    ContactUsRepo
    Repository interface for managing ContactUs entities.
    CorsConfig
    Configuration class for CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing) settings.
    DevCorsConfig
    Development-specific CORS configuration class.
    GlobalExceptionController
    Global exception handler for the application.
    Grants
    Represents a grant in the system, which includes details such as the grant's name, the amount of money available, eligibility criteria, and a description.
    GrantsApplicationController
    REST controller for managing grant applications for the Nausicaä Green Global Initiative.
    GrantsApplicationService
    Service interface for managing grants applications.
    GrantsApplicationServiceImpl
    Implementation of the GrantsApplicationService interface.
    GrantsController
    REST controller for managing grants in the Nausicaä Green Global Initiative.
    GrantsDto
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) for holding grant details in the Green Global Initiative API.
    GrantsRepo
    Repository interface for managing Grants entities.
    GrantsService
    Service interface for managing grants.
    GrantsServiceImpl
    Service implementation for handling grants-related operations.
    JwtFilter
    A filter class that intercepts incoming HTTP requests to validate JWT tokens.
    JwtUtil
    Utility class that handles operations related to JWT (JSON Web Token), such as generating, extracting information, and validating tokens.
    LoginRequest
    Request DTO for user login in the Green Global Initiative API.
    NausicaaGreenInitiativeApplication
    Main application class for the Nausicaa Green Initiative API.
    ProdCorsConfig
    Configuration class for CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing) settings in the production environment.
    QueryController
    REST controller for managing "Contact Us" queries.
    QueryCreateRequest
    Request DTO for creating a new query in the Green Global Initiative API.
    QueryService
    Service interface for handling queries related to contact requests.
    QueryServiceImpl
    Implementation of the QueryService interface.
    ResourceNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when a requested resource is not found.
    SecurityConfig
    Configuration class for Spring Security settings.
    UserController
    REST controller for managing user-related operations.
    UserDetails
    Represents a user's details in the system, including personal information such as their name, email, password, admin status, and last login timestamp.
    UserDetailsDto
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) for holding user details in the Green Global Initiative API.
    UserDetailsRepo
    Repository interface for managing UserDetails entities.
    UserService
    Service interface for handling user-related operations.
    UserServiceImpl
    Implementation of the UserService interface.
